\f1\b \cf0 MUSHROOMS
\f0\b0 \
13.3g / 1 tbsp olive oil\
45g / 3 tbsp butter, unsalted\
12.6g / 1 1/2 tsp garlic, finely minced (~1 large or 2 medium cloves)\
400g / 14oz mushrooms, sliced 3mm / \uc0\u8539 " thick (white/button or Swiss/Cremini)\
6g / 1/4 tsp salt\
1g / 1/8 tsp black pepper\
\

\f1\b GRAVY
\f0\b0 \
30g / 2 tbsp butter, unsalted\
30g / 4 tbsp AP flour\
2 cups beef stock/broth, low-sodium, the best you can find\
